                  "ordered": true,
                  "type": "list"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "The challenge stage for the character can be unlocked using 2",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "text",
                      "ep_id": 6279,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-webstatic.hoyoverse.com/event-static-hoyowiki-admin/2024/07/16/6b1a6516de14a050f6ec44de888a89dc_6777332885926164057.png",
                      "menu_id": 9,
                      "name": "Key of Echoes",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ". After unlocking the stage, it will not require any Keys for any subsequent challenges of the same stage but the challenge will only be accessible when both requirements are met.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "left",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/08/27/41133912/160b26d9fbc7cd327e4d7461378cb76e_8009572621343506825.png"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "Keys of Echoes can be obtained in 2 methods.",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "1. Travelers will receive",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "2",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "Keys initially.",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "2. Complete and finalize",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "Act 6",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "in the",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 225, 75)"
                      ],
                      "text": "Normal Difficulty",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "in",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "each season of the",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "text",
                      "ep_id": 5832,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/04/41133912/ddcd00db3613c8c39ed4d902cc43cc2e_7623522857361033099.png",
                      "menu_id": 14,
                      "name": "Imaginarium Theater",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "to receive",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "1",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "Key.",
                      "type": "text"
